@database MonthNavigatorClass
@index "Classes.guide/Main"

@Node Main "RxMUI - MonthNavigator Class"


MonthNavigator class    @{"Index" link "Classes.guide/Main"} @{"Super" link "AreaClass.guide/Main"}
@{u}                                                             @{uu}

  The MonthNavigator class shows a field with the days of a
  specified month in a specified year.

  MonthNavigator class is a subclass of MonthNavigator.mcc, so
  you must have MonthNavigator.mcc in MUI:Libs/MUI to use it.
  MonthNavigator.mcc is copyright of Kai Hofmann.

  @{u}                                                        @{uu}

 @{b}Attributes@{ub}

  @{fg shine}Day@{fg text}
  N SG

  @{fg shine}MNInputMode@{fg text}
  M I
  One of:
     o Immediate
     o None
     o RelVerify

  @{fg shine}Month@{fg text}
  N ISG

  @{fg shine}Year@{fg text}
  N ISG

  @{u}                                                        @{uu}


 @{b}Methods@{ub}

  None defined

@EndNode
